name: .JTBACKUP File Extension
summary: Learn about .JTBACKUP files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: File created by Just Type, an iOS app used for storing personal notes; saves a backup copy of notes the user has selected and can be restored to put the notes back if they are lost.

content: You can create a backup in Just Type by long pressing the list view, selecting notes, clicking the action button, choosing Email Backup, and then tapping the "Email as Backup" button. A new email will be created with a JTBACKUP file as an attachment.
NOTE: Just Type is no longer available for download.
